# Compound Engineering

When completing any task, if the approach, prompt, or pattern could be reused 
in future sessions, flag it:
"💡 This could be saved as a [skill/command/prompt] in personal-ai — want me 
to draft it?"

Look for:
- A reusable instruction set → personal-ai/skills/
- A reusable prompt → personal-ai/prompts/
- A repo-specific Claude Code command → .claude/commands/
- A repo-specific Cursor rule → .cursor/rules/
- A project convention → relevant CLAUDE.md

Only flag things that would meaningfully improve a future session. Don't flag 
obvious or generic patterns.

Confirm what was created when done.
